  "instructions": [
    "in a large mixing bowl, combine the orange juice, honey, lemon zest, lemon juice, and olive oil.",
    "stir in the flour, salt, and cornstarch until a smooth batter forms.",
    "gradually add the water to the batter and stir until well combined.",
    "cover the batter and let it rest for 30 minutes.",
    "heat the oil in a deep frying pan to 350°F (175°C).",
    "carefully drop the sevaiiya batter by tablespoonfuls into the hot oil.",
    "fry the sevaiiyas until golden brown, about 2-3 minutes on each side.",
    "using a slotted spoon, remove the fritters from the oil and drain on paper towels.",
    "serve the citrusy gooey greek sevaiiya fritters warm and enjoy!"
